title: Dumpling soup (Mandu-guk: 만두국)
description:
Today I’m going to show you a really delicious one bowl meal recipe that you’ll love, especially if you already made my shrimp and chive mandu recipe and have some dumplings in the freezer! This is dumpling soup (Mandu-guk: 만두국)! full recipe: http://www.maangchi.com/recipe/mandu-guk
